<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>403 - Forbidden</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-zinc-950 text-amber-500 font-mono min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="max-w-md w-full p-8 border border-amber-500/50 bg-zinc-900 rounded-lg text-center">
        <div class="text-6xl mb-4">⚠️</div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Access Denied</h1>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm mb-6">
            Security Clearance Level: <span class="text-white font-bold">{{ role }}</span>
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-black/50 p-4 rounded text-left text-xs text-amber-700 mb-6">
            <p>> ERR_INSUFFICIENT_PERMISSIONS</p>
            <p>> Checking session signature... <span class="text-emerald-600">VALID</span></p>
            <p>> Checking role requirement... <span class="text-red-600">FAILED</span></p>
            <p>> Administrator role required for /admin access.</p>
        </div>

        <a href="/" class="text-sm border border-amber-500 px-4 py-2 hover:bg-amber-500 hover:text-black transition-all">
            RETURN TO GATEWAY
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
